      "content": "idk im just really busy with work right now and the clinic is gonna take forever. it doesn't feel like a \"serious injury\" although, it just feels like a bad twist. if i just take some ibuprofen and keep it elevated for like 48 hours, thats probably enough to tell the difference between a sprain and a break, right?",
